Sheet Information

KPI Definition

#{Cases per Process Variant: }
#{Number of Cases per Process Variant. A Variant aggregates all activities of a case, which represents a variant of the process.}

#{AVG # Steps per Case: }
#{Average Number of Activities in one Case}

#{Undesired Activity Rate: }
#{Share of Purchase Order Items, in which at least one Undesired Activity (user defined) has happened.}

#{Repeated Activity Rate: }
#{Share of Purchase Order Items in which Activities (user defined) have happened more than once..}

#{Automation Rate: }
#{Share of Activities completed automatically (by a batch system user). Calculated as # Activities (Automated) divided by # Activities (Automated) plus # Activities (Manual). }

#{Total Cycle Time in Days: }
#{Time between Process Start and Process End in Days.}

#{Subprocess Cycle Time in Days: }
#{Time between two activities in Days. From which activity the calculated Cycle Time should start and at which it should end can be configured through range specifiers.}

variables.title: TIMEFRAME
variables.variableValue:
CASE
WHEN MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT") IN (10,11,12) THEN YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT") || ' - Q1'
WHEN MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT") IN (1,2,3) THEN YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT") || ' - Q2'
WHEN MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT") IN (4,5,6) THEN YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT" ) || ' - Q3'
WHEN MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT") IN (7,8,9) THEN YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT") || ' - Q4'
ELSE NULL
END

variables.title: TIMEFRAME
variables.variableValue:
CASE -- 2 digit Month
WHEN MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT") >= 10
THEN YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT") ||'-' || MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT")
ELSE YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT") ||'-0' || MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT")
END

variables.title: TIMEFRAME
variables.variableValue:
CASE
WHEN CALENDAR_WEEK("VBAK"."ERDAT") >= 10
THEN YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT")
--- ADD one Year if we are already in CW 1 at the end of December
+ CASE WHEN MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT") = 12 AND CALENDAR_WEEK("VBAK"."ERDAT") = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
|| '-CW-' ||CALENDAR_WEEK("VBAK"."ERDAT")
ELSE YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT") || '-CW-0' ||CALENDAR_WEEK("VBAK"."ERDAT")
END

variables.title: TIMEFRAME
variables.variableValue:
CASE -- 2 digit Month
WHEN MONTH( "VBAK"."ERDAT" ) >= 10
THEN CASE
WHEN DAY("VBAK"."ERDAT" ) >= 10
THEN YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT" ) ||'-'|| MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT" ) ||'-' || DAY("VBAK"."ERDAT" )
ELSE YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT" ) ||'-'|| MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT" ) ||'-0' || DAY("VBAK"."ERDAT" )
END
ELSE CASE
WHEN DAY("VBAK"."ERDAT" ) >= 10
THEN YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT" ) ||'-0'|| MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT" ) ||'-' || DAY("VBAK"."ERDAT" )
ELSE YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT" ) ||'-0'|| MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT" ) ||'-0' || DAY("VBAK"."ERDAT" )
END
END
